Number of deaths and population by sex and age groups for Canada in 2023

CanadaDeaths2023.Rd

Number of deaths and population by sex and age groups for Canada in 2023

Usage

CanadaDeaths2023

Format

`CanadaDeaths2023` A data frame with 21 rows and 6 columns:

start

age in years at start of age interval

end

age in years at end of age interval

population.female

female population in the age interval on 2023-07-01

population.male

male population in the age interval on 2023-07-01

deaths.female

number of females in the age interval dying during 2023

deaths.male

number of males in the age interval dying during 2023

Source

Statistics Canada; deaths https://doi.org/10.25318/1310070901-eng; population https://doi.org/10.25318/1710000501-eng; downloaded 2025-01-22.
